        "type": "message",
        "text": "I'll add that I think if the test is creating a whole blog post or something, that should be paid — and maybe even used. Once I worked at a place hiring for a position, and interviewees were writing on the same topic as the blog post I was writing at the time. Why do five of us need to write it?",
